layers.nm: Society should be cautious about the amount of responsiblity they give to digital entities and what consequences may occur because of it.

s.t: Society should be cautious about the amount of responsiblity they give to digital entities and what consequences may occur because of it.

layers.nm: TLDR: Humans should not have complete trust in A.I. systems, as they have been and will continually be built upon human biases and human-based data and are developed by humanity.
